$lang['Just like in decimal, after 16 symbols have been used in Hexadecimal, the order of numbers starts over again at zero. So, hexadecimal 10 is equal to decimal 16, and hexadecimal 11 is equal to decimal 17. And so on!'] = 'E like me ka decimal, ma hope o ka hoʻohana ʻia ʻana o nā hōʻailona he 16 i ka Hexadecimal, hoʻomaka hou ke ʻano o nā helu ma ka ʻole. No laila, ua like ka hexadecimal 10 me ka decimal 16, a ua like ka hexadecimal 11 me ka decimal 17. A pela aku!';
